---
interface Props {
  techCount: number;
  essaysCount: number;
}

const { techCount, essaysCount } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="relative mb-12 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 via-indigo-50 to-purple-50 py-16 px-6 md:py-24 md:px-16">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute -right-48 -top-48 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-blue-200/30 blur-3xl animate-float" />
    <div class="absolute right-16 top-16 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-indigo-200/25 blur-3xl animate-float" style="animation-delay: 2s" />
    <div class="absolute -bottom-32 left-1/4 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-purple-200/20 blur-3xl animate-float" style="animation-delay: 4s" />
    <div class="absolute left-12 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 h-48 w-48 rounded-full bg-cyan-200/20 blur-3xl animate-float" style="animation-delay: 1s" />
  </div>

  <div class="absolute top-8 right-8 flex h-40 w-40 items-center justify-center md:top-12 md:right-16 md:h-56 md:w-56">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 animate-spin-slow opacity-20" style="animation: spin 30s linear infinite">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border-2 border-dashed border-blue-400" />
      <div class="absolute inset-6 rounded-full border-2 border-dashed border-indigo-400" />
      <div class="absolute inset-12 rounded-full border-2 border-dashed border-purple-400" />
    </div>
    <div class="relative flex h-24 w-24 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white/80 shadow-lg backdrop-blur-sm md:h-32 md:w-32">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl">📝</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/70 px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-blue-600 shadow-sm mb-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
      <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse" />
      持续更新中
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
      安静地记录
      <span class="relative inline-block">
        <span class="relative z-10 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-indigo-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">技术与生活</span>
        <span class="absolute -bottom-1 left-0 h-2 w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-200 via-indigo-200 to-purple-200 rounded-full" />
      </span>
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg text-gray-600 md:text-xl">
      关于云原生、Linux、数据库和长期主义的思考，记录每一次学习与成长。
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl bg-white/80 px-5 py-3 shadow-sm backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-blue-100">
          <span class="text-lg">💻</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">技术文章</p>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">{techCount} 篇</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl bg-white/80 px-5 py-3 shadow-sm backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-purple-100">
          <span class="text-lg">✍️</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">随笔</p>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">{essaysCount} 篇</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a
        href="#posts"
        class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-blue-200 transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        开始阅读
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">
          <path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a
        href="/rss.xml"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-gray-200 bg-white/80 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 shadow-sm backdrop-blur-sm transition-all hover:border-blue-300 hover:text-blue-600 hover:shadow-md"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M4 12a8 8 0 0 1 8-8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 7.5 4.75 8 8 0 0 1-4.5 11.25" />
          <path d="M12 18a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6" />
        </svg>
        订阅更新
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style is:global>
  @keyframes spin {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }
</style>
